PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Canadian Heritage of THELMA ANN BRENNAN of Johnville, New Brunswick, as a trustee of the Board of Trustees of the Canadian Museum of Civilization to hold office during pleasusre for a term of three years, in the place of Gloria C.
